org.gsma.joyn.vsh
Class VideoRenderer

java.lang.Object
  IVideoRenderer.Stub
      org.gsma.joyn.vsh.VideoRenderer

public abstract class VideoRenderer
extends IVideoRenderer.Stub

Video renderer offers an interface to manage the video renderer instance independently of the joyn service. The video renderer is implemented in the application side. The video renderer receives the video streaming over the network in RTP, decodes the video frames and displays the decoded picture on the device screen.

Author:
Jean-Marc AUFFRET
